{{version030}}
{{flavour|The Depths are the deepest part of the dungeon proper, subject to the corrupting influence of the Realm of Zot without being considered a part of it.}}

[[File:Depths entry.png]] '''The Depths''' are a four-floor [[branch]] accessed through a guarded portal on [[Dungeon]]:15. Its layout generally resembles that of the Dungeon, although it has a greater tendency toward open spaces and elaborate full floor [[vault]]s. Along with several entrances to [[the Abyss]], [[the Vestibule of Hell]], and [[Pandemonium]] and an entrance to a [[Ziggurat]], you can find the entrance to [[the Realm of Zot]] on Depths:4, guarded by a variety of [[list of draconians|draconian]] guards.

==Portals==
*[[File:Abyss entry.png]] A portal to [[the Abyss]] always spawns on Depths:3. Other Depths floors have a 33% chance to have a portal.
*[[File:Hell entry.png]] An entrance to the [[Vestibule of Hell]] appears on every Depths floor.
*[[File:Ziggurat portal.png]] One [[ziggurat]] portal spawns on a random Depths floor.
*[[File:Pandemonium entry.png]] A portal to the [[Pandemonium]] always spawns on Depths:2. Other Depths floors have a 25% chance to have a portal.

==Strategy==
Generally, it isn't advised for you to enter the Depths right after you complete D:15. There are easier areas available ([[Lair]] and its branches, [[Orcish Mines]], and [[The Vaults]]).

